name: Vessels 167: Story Beat 07
description:
4) …And holds it to his ear. Slowly and with great difficulty he’s made his way vaguely upright on the sofa. He’s cradling his aching head in one hand, holding the phone to his ear with the other.
ROBERT: THE FUCK DO YOU WANT?
VOICE FROM PHONE: HER MAJESTY DEMANDS YOUR PRESENCE IMMEDIATELY.
5) Closer on Robert’s look of concern.
ROBERT (INTERNAL): AH, FUCK.
ROBERT: INFORM HER MAJESTY I AM ON MY WAY.
6) Robert stands and stares down at the bottles on the floor around him.
ROBERT (INTERNAL): WHAT THE FUCK HAPPENED LAST NIGHT, ROBERT?
